Directed by Raja Menon.

Written by Ritesh Shah. Suresh Nair. Raja Menon.

Cast Saif Ali Khan(Roshan Kalra). Padmapriya(Radha Menon (as Padmapriya Janakiraman)). Svar Kamble(Arman). Chandan Roy Sanyal(Nuzroon).Dinesh P. Nair. Milind Soman(Biju). Sobhita Dhulipala(Vinnie). Ram Gopal Bajaj(Roshan’s Father). Pawan Chopra(Sunil manhori).Avtaar Singh Sahani. Vikraman Nair(Kochi: Drunkard). Ramachandran P.P.(Kochi: Anil Ettan). M. Gopalakrishnan(Kochi: Union Leader). Jayan Cherthala(Kochi: Old Mallu Customer). K.V. Srikanth Menon(Kochi: Bala). Archana S. Menon(Kochi: Bala’s Wife). Babitha Shijith(Kochi: Radha’s Artist Friend). Vishnu Vijayan(Kochi: Radha’s Other Friend). Noorudheen Valayamkulam(Kochi: Radha’s Servant). Santhakumari N.N.(Kochi: Radha’s Cook). Anil Kumar P.P.(Kochi: Radha’s Driver). Neha Saxena(Kochi: Honeymooning Wife). Sardar Simar Nagra(Kochi: Honeymooning Husband). Bhaskaran Pillai. N.(Kochi: Old Man on Bus). Ajita Kulkarni(Kochi: Parent #1). Rihana Vora(Kochi: Parent #2). Eshanika Mehta(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Gehna Khaturia(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Shlok Tejwani(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Nidhhi Agerwal(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid (as Nidhi Agarwal)). Ziyan Noorani(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Soha Chatterjee(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Eshaan Sood(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Aahana Barmecha(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Aksshat Barmecha(Kochi: Back Stage Dancer Kid). Raghu Dixit(Goa: Raghu Dixit). Gaurav Vaz(Goa: Raghu’s Band Member). Joman Jacob Joseph(Goa: Raghu’s Band Member). Sanjay Kumar(Goa: Raghu’s Band Member). Varun.V. Bandekar(Goa: Customer #2). Rajat Ajay Bose(Goa: Customer #3). Dylan Fernandes(Goa: Proposal Man). Dawn C.J. Mortimer(Goa: Proposal Woman). Shaurya Chopra(Delhi: Young Roshan). Riju Bajaj(Delhi: Young Inderjeet). Nishad Raj Rana(Delhi: Cop). Kapil Punjabi(Delhi: Cabbie). Abhishek Kumar(Amritsar: Dhaba Waiter). Lokesh Mittal(Amritsar: Dhaba Owner’s Son). Michael Kelberg(New York: Angry Galli Customer). Danish Karthik(New York: Fahad Hussain (as Dhanish Karthik)). Rob(New York: Bartender). Pavitran Nambiar(New York: Galli’s Kitchen Chef). Himanshu Taneja(New York: Galli’s Kitchen Chef). Shahnawaz Quereshi(New York: Galli’s Kitchen Chef). Matteo Arvonio(New York: Galli’s Kitchen Chef). Varun Basur(New York: Galli’s Kitchen Chef). Vishwas Shetty(New York: Galli’s Kitchen Chef). Jackey Mishra(Staff). Dinesh Prabhakar(Alex)

Language Hindi.

Producers Badal Singh Bhandari. Dilip Borkar. Hanif Chunawala. Priti Gulati. Priya Gupta. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Vikram Malhotra. Raja Menon. Shijith Purushothaman. Janani Ravichandran. Eldho Selvaraj. Atit Shah. Shikhaa Sharma. Daljit Singh.

Production Abundantia Entertainment. Bandra West Pictures. Create Entertainment.
